> @cevich any ideas? Ubuntu keeps failing with locking conflicts on apt.

@rhatdan   Oh yes, thanks for reminding me.  I fixed this in the cache-images for libpod, but here and in buildah we're using the base-images.  I've got it on my TODO list to flip to using the cache-images here (and in buildah) which will eliminate this (very annoying) problem.

If that doesn't work out (for some reason), I'll have to apply the fix to the base-images.  This is possible, but much more difficult and not fully automate-able.
